soldier is a 1998 american science fiction action film directed by paul w. s. anderson , written by david webb peoples , and starring kurt russell , jason scott lee , jason isaacs , connie nielsen , sean pertwee and gary busey . the film tells the story of a highly skilled genetically advanced soldier &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; his commanders and facing a relentless and brutal rival soldier . the film was released worldwide on october 23 , 1998 . upon its release , soldier received generally negative reviews but many praised the action sequences and russell 's performance . the film was a commercial failure , grossing $ 14 million worldwide against a production budget of $ 60 million .